  <summary>A fun 2D retro platformer inspired by Sonic games and a game creation system</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      A fun 2D retro platformer inspired by Sonic games and a
      game creation system that lets you unleash your creativity!
    </p>
    <p>
      Make your dreams come true! Create your own amazing games with
      our game engine and learn programming with SurgeScript, a
      scripting language for games that is fun to use! Create new levels,
      items, bosses, playable characters, gameplay mechanics, cutscenes
      and much more!
    </p>
    <p>
      Surge the Rabbit is fun for all ages! You will stop the global
      takeover planned by evil wizard Gimacian the Dark in a fantastic
      adventure! ...and you will also get to create your own universes
      with our open source game engine!
    </p>
  </description>
